front_matter:
  id: pm-cnil
  title: Optimize test-all dedupe across timeout variants
  description: "Ensure test-all executes identical linked command/path only once even when timeout metadata differs, to keep closed-sweep regressions bounded."
  type: Task
  status: closed
  priority: 1
  tags[6]: "area:testing",code,"milestone:6",pm-cli,"priority:1",tests
  created_at: "2026-03-06T21:31:15.657Z"
  updated_at: "2026-03-06T21:47:11.037Z"
  deadline: "2026-03-08T18:00:00.000Z"
  author: maintainer-agent
  estimated_minutes: 90
  acceptance_criteria: "pm test-all deduplicates by scope+command/path identity regardless of timeout metadata, chooses a deterministic effective timeout, reports deterministic duplicate skips, and tests/docs reflect behavior."
  comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
    "2026-03-06T21:31:15.657Z",maintainer-agent,"Why this exists: release sweeps run too long due to timeout-variant duplicate linked tests."
    "2026-03-06T21:31:23.205Z",maintainer-agent,"Planned change-set: align docs and implementation so test-all dedupe key ignores timeout metadata and uses deterministic effective timeout when running the retained command."
    "2026-03-06T21:34:08.029Z",maintainer-agent,"Implemented: test-all now computes a per-key effective timeout (max timeout_seconds across duplicates) before execution, while still emitting duplicate skipped results deterministically. Updated PRD/README/AGENTS contract text and added unit coverage for timeout-variant duplicate commands."
    "2026-03-06T21:35:44.535Z",maintainer-agent,"Verification note: initial full coverage run failed at 99.96% due to uncovered helper branch in src/cli/commands/test-all.ts. Applied follow-up refactor to remove dead branch structure and keep timeout maxing logic deterministic."
    "2026-03-06T21:37:12.970Z",maintainer-agent,Added unit test for equal-timeout duplicate command entries (different notes) to cover deterministic timeout conflict path and restore 100% coverage gate.
    "2026-03-06T21:47:10.731Z",maintainer-agent,"Evidence: pm test pm-cnil --run passed (tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts, 7/7). node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed with 100% statements/branches/functions/lines. pm test-all --status in_progress passed (1 item, failed=0). pm test-all --status closed passed (107 items, linked_tests=296, passed=63, failed=0, skipped=233)."
  notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
    "2026-03-06T21:31:15.657Z",maintainer-agent,"Plan: update docs then test-all keying logic and unit coverage; verify via sandbox-safe run-tests."
  files[5]{path,scope,note}:
    AGENTS.md,project,agent workflow note for timeout-aware test-all dedupe
    PRD.md,project,authoritative test-all dedupe timeout contract
    README.md,project,document timeout conflict resolution in test-all dedupe
    src/cli/commands/test-all.ts,project,dedupe key and timeout selection logic
    tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts,project,coverage for timeout-variant dedupe
  tests[1]{command,path,scope,timeout_seconds,note}:
    node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts,null,project,1200,targeted command coverage
  docs[3]{path,scope,note}:
    AGENTS.md,project,maintainer workflow contract
    PRD.md,project,command contract for test-all dedupe semantics
    README.md,project,public command behavior contract
  close_reason: test-all duplicate timeout resolution implemented and verified; docs updated; regression sweeps passed
body: Observed release-maintenance sweeps can trigger repeated execution of identical linked test commands when only timeout_seconds differs across historical items. This creates very long runs and weakens regression-loop usability.
